==English==

===Noun===
'''determinism'''

# {{cat|Ethics}}(''Ethics'') The doctrine that all actions are determined by the current state and immutable laws of the universe, with no possibility of choice.
# {{computing}} The property of having behavior determined only by initial state and input.

